UML:TaggedValue.value: IF_GellValuePair has the geometry IF_Surface. IF_Surface is a data type that inherits from both GM_Polygon and CV_GridCell establishing rectangular grid cells as the discrete surface coverage elements.
The attribute domainExtent shall contain the extent of the spatiotemporal domain of the coverage. The data type EX_Extent, is defined in ISO 19103. Extents may be specified in both space and time.
